'''ReText''' is a simple but powerful text editor for '''Markdown''' and '''reStructuredText''' with '''"Live preview"''' function

== Installation ==

ReText is not availible in main portage tree, so it is contained in a [http://gpo.zugaina.org/Overlays/gentoo-zh gentoo-zh] Overlay - [http://gpo.zugaina.org/app-text/retext retext] package

{{Note| For more information regarding overlays, please read the [[overlay]] article.}}

Adding overlay:

{{RootCmd| layman --add gentoo-zh}}

Than emerge as standart program:

{{Emerge|retext}}

